---
title: Honey-Glazed Pork & Cucumber Cos Salad with Apple & Herby Mayonnaise
description: Sweet, savoury and oh-so-satisfying! The honey-glazed pork steak is the star of the show, perfectly caramelised and bursting with flavour. Paired with a crisp salad of cos, cucumber and sweet apple, it’s a fresh, vibrant dish that’s as delicious as it is wholesome.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the kohlrabi in this recipe with cucumber due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just
follow your recipe card!*
